stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR

    [*]       --> Active    : 생성 / Reset()\n(mCancelled=false)
    Active    --> Active    : Submit()\nin-flight++\n람다 큐잉
    Active    --> Cancelled : Cancel()\nmCancelled = true

    Cancelled --> Cancelled : Submit()\nfast-path skip\n(in-flight++ 후 즉시 --)
    Cancelled --> Drained   : WaitForDrain()\nmInFlight == 0

    Drained   --> [*]       : ~AsyncScope()\nRAII 자동 정리
    Drained   --> Active    : Reset()\n풀 재사용 경로

    note right of Cancelled
        Submit 이후 큐잉된 람다는
        실행 시점에 IsCancelled()를
        재확인하여 skip
    end note
